{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_11_02",
  "title": "佐伯遙子",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――現在",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "懐かしいわね。麻奈ちゃんのバースデーライブ\nあの時、手伝うと決めて本当に良かったわ",
      "startTime": 7.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.866666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんも喜んでくれたし、ファンの子達とも\n仲良くなれたし。あの時の一体感は忘れられないわ",
      "startTime": 14.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.866666619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "俺は、遙子さんがゲストとしてステージに立つ姿も\n見てみたかったです",
      "startTime": 23.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってくれるのは嬉しいんだけど\nあの頃の私はね、かなり焦っていたの",
      "startTime": 31.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.9333332856
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "私よりも後にデビューした麻奈ちゃんが\nどんどん先に行っちゃって……",
      "startTime": 39.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "なんとか追いつきたくて\nいろいろと挑戦してみたけど、全然うまくいかなくて",
      "startTime": 43.8288642906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "そんな時に、麻奈ちゃんからバースデーライブの\nゲストの話をもらって、凄く嬉しかったわ",
      "startTime": 51.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "でも、同時に思ったの。いくらゲストとはいえ\n今の私が大切なステージに上がってもいいのかって",
      "startTime": 62.3137868959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "例え、ステージに上がったとしても\n麻奈ちゃんやみんなに、胸を張ることが出来るのかって",
      "startTime": 70.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.1999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……\nだからあの時、ゲスト出演を断ったんですね",
      "startTime": 76.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.1999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。そのかわり、来年までには成長して\nステージの上でお祝いするって心に決めていたわ",
      "startTime": 85.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "つまらないプライドだとは思うけど\nそれでも私には、大切なことだったから",
      "startTime": 92.4942162878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.5999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "つまらなくなんてないですよ。あいつも\n遙子さんのことを、かっこいいって言ってました",
      "startTime": 99.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈は遙子さんの気持ちに気付いていたんだと思います\n割り切って、それでも前に進もうとする気持ちに",
      "startTime": 106.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.8999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんが……。そっか、そうだったのね……\nふふ、アイドル同士、分かっちゃうのかもしれないわね",
      "startTime": 122.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.9999999523
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "……ねぇ、{user}君\nあの時の『来年』は、結局来なかったけれど……",
      "startTime": 130.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "今の私なら、立ってもいいのかしら\n……今更、遅いかもしれないけどね",
      "startTime": 141.7333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない、って麻奈なら言うと思いますよ？",
      "startTime": 144.8666717052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.8666717052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それこそ、今度の月ストのライブでもいいと思います\nゲストとして、ステージに立っても",
      "startTime": 154.1000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんのお誕生日に、私がゲストで……",
      "startTime": 156.6000050385,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6900.00004769999,
          "startTime": 163.5000050862
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.6000050385
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "startTime": 162.4666717052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 163.4000050862
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 163.4000050862
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね\n仕事終わりに、わざわざ付き合ってもらっちゃって",
      "startTime": 165.7000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、今日の予定はこれで最後でしたから\nでも、なんでここに？",
      "startTime": 172.9821594046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "バースデーライブの後に、麻奈ちゃんが遊びに\n誘ってくれてね。その時に、ここに来たの",
      "startTime": 180.6666717529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "ライブが終わったばっかりだったのに\n麻奈ちゃん、すっごく元気でね……",
      "startTime": 188.3000101725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくだから、その時に私個人で\nお誕生日のお祝いもしたんだけど……",
      "startTime": 194.0333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "その時、麻奈ちゃん、言ってたんだ\n「私も遙子ちゃんにプレゼント用意するからね」って",
      "startTime": 201.4000071207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 206.7666737873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "お祝いのお返しに、遙子さんの誕生日にも\nプレゼントを用意する、ってことでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 211.333340454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "私も、その時はそう思っていたんだけど、違ったみたい\nあのライブの後、麻奈ちゃんが出した曲、覚えてる？",
      "startTime": 221.4666737873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
      "startTime": 227.0667093435
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "『voyage』……\n夢に向かって頑張る人への応援ソング、ですね",
      "startTime": 229.0000071207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_02-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "本人に聞いた訳じゃないんだけど、もしかしたら\nあの曲が私へのプレゼントだったのかなって思ってるの",
      "startTime": 237.433340454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_themepark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-night",
